Insider Activity


Individual




Michael Levit



Mr. Michael Levit is on the Board of Directors at August Home, Inc. Mr. Levit was previously employed as a Principal by A.V.M. Software, Inc., a Principal by Accenture LLP, a Principal by HearMe, a Principal by Historic AOL LLC, a Principal by Kmart Corp., and Executive VP-Marketing & Business Development by Vendio Services, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of California, Santa Barbara and a graduate degree from the University of Oxford.



