 of two categories.  Applications will be selected by a non-partisan committee panel. The application deadline is Friday September 29th, 2017 at 5 p.m. To apply or request an application package reach out directly to my office at 416-638-3700 or email michael.levitt@parl.gc.ca. Once an application is filled out please send it to michael.levitt@parl.gc.ca or mail applications to: Michael Levitt, MP 660 Wilson Ave. North York ON M3K1E1 The awards will be presented at a ceremony on Sunday October 29th, 2017. Location and timing will be provided at a later date.  Come join us in our celebration of Canada! 展开Michael Levitt MP 在 St. Bernard's Residence · 昨天 09:33 · 加拿大 · Ontario · 多伦多 · Had a wonderful visit to St. Bernard's Residence to meet with students employed thru the Canada Summer Jobs Program in York Centre and hear about their experiences.全部帖子Michael Levitt MP · 在 Kiva's Bagels · 觉得快乐 · 昨天 05:25 · 加拿大 · Ontario · 多伦多 · A great way to start the week at Kiva's in York Centre. #HappyMondayMichael Levitt MP · 7月22日 16:23 · I reaffirm the condemnation of this brutal terror attack that claimed the lives of three members of the Salomon family, as they joined together for Shabbat dinner. My thoughts are w/ the family and friends of the victims of this appalling act. May their memories forever be a blessing.Michael Levitt MP 分享了帖子 · 7月21日 10:57 · 3 weeks to go to our Annual Community BBQ! Live music and free lunch at Downsview Park. Did you register? https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/mp-michael-levitts-annual-commu…Michael Levitt MP 将链接分享至活动：MP Michael Levitt's Annual Community BBQ · 7月21日 10:55 · Melodia de Bolivia will be performing at our Annual Community BBQ! Remember, live music, face painting, hot dogs and burgers in Downsview Park on Sunday, August... 13th starting at 12 pm. First come, first served! Register here: https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/mp-michael-levitts-annual-commu… 展开MELODIA DE BOLIVIAGRUPO DE DANZA MELODIA DE BOLIVIA, EN TORONTO, CANADA.youtube.comMichael Levi